:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">풀버스트 발동 후 양 옆에 나오는 아픈 랩처 (모노아이) 5마리 제거</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 수니스 2스는 공 높은 적에게 하는 거라 가운데에 있는 진짜 잡몹에게 안날라감</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 6마리 제거 해도 되지만 보통 처음에 랩처가 겹쳐있어서 죽을때 있으므로 안전하게 5마리만 제거 추천</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">잡몹 다 안죽이는 이유</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">-&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">대략 7마리 이상 죽이면 풀버중에 아가리 나와서 망함</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">5~6마리만 제거 하고 전체 엄폐</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">풀버 0.5초 남았을때 전체 엄폐 풀고 남은 잡몹 잡기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">2. 레후 - 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed98930b7cbc843b2e963105912857e25a7882ba6ae20158b1a94bb526972c6b5bd48714\" alt=\"a64319aa372a782a907e5c6dc6836a2d91706ebc8dc1fb1220ea35adab61\"></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">최대한 빠르게 버충하면서 남은 잡몹 다 잡으면 좋음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">그 후 양 옆에&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">랩처 (모노아이) 나오기 전에 풀버스트</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 나오고 풀버 쓰면 신데렐라 순차공격에 저 랩처도 맞음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 그러면 바로 다음 아가리 나와서 망함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">신데렐라 버스트로 양옆 터지는 랩처는 자동 제거</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">그 후 아가리 랩처 코어부분 말고 윗 부분 조준</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 잡몹을 안죽이기 위함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">풀버 6초 되기 전까지 아가리 &amp; 잡몹 잡으면 안됨</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 1마리라도 잡히면 다음 잡몹 나오면서 아가리 나와서 망함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">풀버스트 6초 미만이 될 때 아가리 제거 &amp; 잡몹 제거</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">그 후 잡몹도 잡으면서 다음 아가리 조준</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">3. 라후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">빠르게 버충하고 풀버</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">공중 랩처 6마리 제거 -&gt; 아가리 제거 -&gt; 남은 버스트로 남은 엘리트 (아이벡스) 최대한 피 깎기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">4. 레후 - 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">신데렐라 재장전 시켜주기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed98930b7cbc843b2e963105fc4555e150798bbf68d504e8894d927c1fa8e17c6f6d94ec59\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\" alt=\"a17c00aa2132b55396350e6558c12a3a780b14c5805c879d3b3cc162\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">크라운이나 신데렐라로 십자가 부분 조준해놓기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 레후 조작해서 톡톡이 해도 되는데 다음 웨이브때 나오는 첫 엘리트로 조준되서 약간 딜로스</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 딜 부족하면 이때 조준보정 풀어서 레후 톡톡이까지 해야할 듯?</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">침묵 랩처 뽑기전에 무조건 잡기</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 침묵 랩처 나오면 그 때 버스트 끝나서 거의 못잡음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">5. 라후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">딱 아가리 잡으면서 풀버 끝나면서 보스 아가리 나옴</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">보스 양 옆에 터지는 랩처 제거 -&gt; 아픈 랩처 (모노아이) 제거 -&gt; 침묵 랩처 제거</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">- 아픈 랩처가 골고루 쏴주길 기도 or 크라운 스택 조절해놓기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">6. 레후 - 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">침묵 랩처 뱉기 전에 풀버</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">보스 조준</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\">중간에 터지는 랩처 나오면 제거 후 다시 보스 조준하면 클리어</span></p>",
